@* هدر فروشگاه — لوگو، جستجو، سبد، ورود/ثبت‌نام، مگامنو. هیچ آیتم «محبوب‌ها». *@
<header class="site-header">
    <div class="header-top">
        <div class="container header-top__inner">
            <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="ماهان شاپ">
                <svg class="brand__mark" width="34" height="34" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l1.5-5h15L21 9"/><path d="M4 9h16v10a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H5a1 1 0 0 1-1-1z"/><path d="M9 13h6"/></svg>
                <span class="brand__name">ماهان شاپ</span>
            </a>

            <form class="search" role="search" action="/search" method="get">
                <svg class="search__icon" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/><path d="M21 21l-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
                <input class="search__input" type="search" name="q" placeholder="جستجوی محصول، برند یا دسته…" aria-label="جستجو" />
            </form>

            <div class="header-actions">
                <a class="icon-btn search-trigger d-lg-none" href="/search" aria-label="جستجو">
                    <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/><path d="M21 21l-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
                </a>

                <div class="cart-wrap">
                    <a class="icon-btn cart-btn" href="/cart" aria-label="سبد خرید">
                        <svg class="cart-ico" width="23" height="23" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
                            <path d="M2.5 3.5h2.2l1.2 2m0 0 1.9 9.1a1.6 1.6 0 0 0 1.57 1.27h7.84a1.6 1.6 0 0 0 1.57-1.25l1.46-6.62a.8.8 0 0 0-.78-.97H5.9"/>
                            <circle cx="9.5" cy="20" r="1.5"/>
                            <circle cx="18" cy="20" r="1.5"/>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="cart-badge" data-cart-count hidden>0</span>
                    </a>
                </div>

                @if (User.Identity?.IsAuthenticated == true)
                {
                    <a class="btn-auth" href="/Panel" title="حساب کاربری">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/></svg>
                        <span>@User.Identity!.Name</span>
                    </a>
                    <form asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Logout" method="post" class="d-inline d-lg-block">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-auth btn-auth--logout" title="خروج">
                            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 21H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4"/><path d="M16 17l5-5-5-5"/><path d="M21 12H9"/></svg>
                        </button>
                    </form>
                }
                else
                {
                    <a class="btn-auth" href="/Account/Login">
                        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M4 21a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"/></svg>
                        <span>ورود / ثبت‌نام</span>
                    </a>
                }

                <button class="icon-btn drawer-toggle d-lg-none" type="button" aria-label="باز کردن منو" aria-expanded="false" data-drawer-open>
                    <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M3 6h18M3 12h18M3 18h18"/></svg>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="header-nav d-none d-lg-block">
        <div class="container">
            @await Component.InvokeAsync("CategoryMenu")
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

@* دراور موبایل — از سمت چپ باز می‌شود *@
<div class="drawer" data-drawer hidden>
    <div class="drawer__backdrop" data-drawer-close></div>
    <aside class="drawer__panel" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="منوی موبایل">
        <div class="drawer__head">
            <a class="brand brand--drawer" href="/">
                <svg class="brand__mark" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 9l1.5-5h15L21 9"/><path d="M4 9h16v10a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H5a1 1 0 0 1-1-1z"/><path d="M9 13h6"/></svg>
                <span class="brand__name">ماهان شاپ</span>
            </a>
            <button class="icon-btn" type="button" aria-label="بستن منو" data-drawer-close>
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M6 6l12 12M18 6L6 18"/></svg>
            </button>
        </div>

        <form class="drawer__search" role="search" action="/search" method="get">
            <svg class="search__icon" width="19" height="19" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/><path d="M21 21l-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
            <input class="search__input" type="search" name="q" placeholder="جستجو…" aria-label="جستجو" />
        </form>

        <a class="drawer__all" href="/products">
            <span class="drawer__all-ico" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/></svg>
            </span>
            تمام محصولات
            <svg class="drawer__all-arrow" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
        </a>

        <nav class="drawer__nav">
            @await Component.InvokeAsync("CategoryMenu")
        </nav>

        @if (User.Identity?.IsAuthenticated == true)
        {
            <div class="drawer__foot">
                <a class="btn-primary w-100" href="/Panel">حساب کاربری</a>
                <form asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Logout" method="post" class="mt-2">
                    <button type="submit" class="btn-ghost w-100">خروج</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        }
        else
        {
            <div class="drawer__foot">
                <a class="btn-primary w-100" href="/Account/Login">ورود / ثبت‌نام</a>
            </div>
        }
    </aside>
</div>
